pipeline.py - Financial Hero: End-to-End Short Video Pipeline
=============================================================

Single command to go from a topic to a finished YouTube Short + thumbnail.

Usage
-----
    # Quickest — just a topic, everything auto-generated:
    python pipeline.py --topic "Why the rich get richer"

    # Full control:
    python pipeline.py \\
        --topic   "Why the rich get richer" \\
        --script  "Your custom script here..." \\
        --voice   en-us          \\  # espeak-ng voice (offline, free)
        --speed   148            \\  # words per minute
        --style   split          \\  # thumbnail style: split | dramatic | youtube
        --seed    42             \\  # thumbnail image seed
        --out     output/        \\  # output directory
        --api-key sk-ant-...        # Anthropic key for AI script (optional)

TTS options (all free):
    espeak-ng  — offline, built-in, robotic but reliable  (default, no key needed)
    gtts       — Google TTS, natural voice               (needs internet)
    elevenlabs — best quality                            (needs free API key)

Script generation:
    With  --api-key  → Claude generates a viral finance script
    Without          → built-in template scripts are used
"""

